contentrichtext.text: '''JIT''' may refer to: * Various meanings of [[Just in Time (disambiguation)]]: ** [[Just-in-time compilation]] - a technique for improving the performance of [[virtual machine]]s in [[computing]]. ** [[Just-in-time (business)]] - a [[business]] [[inventory]] strategy. * [[Extensible Messaging and Presence Protocol|Jabber]] ICQ Transport. * [[Jhulelal Institute of Technology]] '''Jit''' may refer to: '''J.I.T.''' '' Juvenile Delinquent in Training'': Southern slang used to describe the "Thug" youth element.
